OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The rules governing the conduct of     
OL,6, ministers and senior civil servants    
OL,7, need to be toughened up, according to a
OL,8, new report.                            
OL,10,FThe Committee on Standards in Public   
OL,11,FLife - which advises the PM on ethical 
OL,12,Fstandards - has been carrying out a    
OL,13,Freview into processes in Westminster.  
OL,15,FIt concluded transparency around       
OL,16,Flobbying was "poor" and the current    
OL,17,Fguidance relied too much on convention.
OL,19,FThe watchdog has recommended to Boris  
OL,20,FJohnson that rules be strengthened.    
